dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This layer shows land areas managed by Snohomish County Parks Department. Boundaries are registered with the Generalized Parcels (PUD).  ParksLand data is updated randomly as new information becomes available. ParksLand is derived from a master data set that contains additional features. Derivative data sets are refreshed when the master is updated.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
